{"label": "droite", "transcript": [{"text": "M\u00eame si vous d\u00e9noncez cette politique des ch\u00e8ques,", "start": 0.049, "duration": 1.65}, {"text": "vous allez l'accompagner", "start": 1.699, "duration": 1.767}, {"text": "pour les plus modestes d'entre nous,", "start": 3.466, "duration": 2.7}, {"text": "quand elle se pose ?", "start": 6.166, "duration": 1.067}, {"text": "- Je pense par exemple", "start": 7.233, "duration": 0.85}, {"text": "\u00e0 la question des retrait\u00e9s,", "start": 8.083, "duration": 1.05}, {"text": "des gens qui ont travaill\u00e9 toute leur vie", "start": 9.133, "duration": 1.566}, {"text": "et qui aujourd'hui", "start": 10.699, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "n'arrivent plus du tout \u00e0 s'en sortir,", "start": 11.299, "duration": 2.1}, {"text": "qui n'arrivent plus", "start": 13.399, "duration": 0.684}, {"text": "\u00e0 faire face \u00e0 l'explosion", "start": 14.083, "duration": 1.533}, {"text": "des prix de l'\u00e9nergie.", "start": 15.616, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "Je pense qu'on n'a pas encore", "start": 16.483, "duration": 1.083}, {"text": "vu le plus dur, malheureusement.", "start": 17.566, "duration": 1.3}, {"text": "Et donc il faut, bien s\u00fbr,", "start": 18.866, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "accompagner ceux qui ne sont pas", "start": 19.966, "duration": 1.9}, {"text": "en situation de travailler", "start": 21.866, "duration": 1.65}, {"text": "parce qu'ils ont d\u00e9j\u00e0 cotis\u00e9", "start": 23.516, "duration": 1.55}, {"text": "pendant toute leur vie.", "start": 25.066, "duration": 0.717}, {"text": "Mais pour les actifs,", "start": 25.783, "duration": 1.5}, {"text": "et c'est, je crois, le sujet majeur,", "start": 27.283, "duration": 2.05}, {"text": "il faut absolument que", "start": 29.333, "duration": 2.216}, {"text": "l'effort de l'\u00c9tat", "start": 31.549, "duration": 0.867}, {"text": "ne consiste pas", "start": 32.416, "duration": 1.35}, {"text": "\u00e0 continuer de multiplier", "start": 33.766, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "les allocations de toutes sortes,", "start": 35.033, "duration": 1.166}, {"text": "mais au contraire \u00e0 redonner du salaire", "start": 36.199, "duration": 2.584}, {"text": "\u00e0 ceux qui travaillent.", "start": 38.899, "duration": 0.934}, {"text": "Ce sera d'ailleurs aussi", "start": 39.833, "duration": 1.166}, {"text": "une mani\u00e8re de sortir", "start": 40.999, "duration": 1.117}, {"text": "notre pays de la situation aberrante", "start": 42.116, "duration": 1.733}, {"text": "dans laquelle nous sommes o\u00f9,", "start": 43.849, "duration": 0.984}, {"text": "alors que nous avons", "start": 44.833, "duration": 0.75}, {"text": "des millions de ch\u00f4meurs en France,", "start": 45.583, "duration": 1.383}, {"text": "quelles que soient", "start": 46.966, "duration": 0.667}, {"text": "les modalit\u00e9s de calcul,", "start": 47.633, "duration": 1.1}, {"text": "vous avez des milliers d'entreprises", "start": 48.733, "duration": 1.9}, {"text": "qui vous disent", "start": 50.633, "duration": 0.5}, {"text": "que leur plus gros probl\u00e8me,", "start": 51.133, "duration": 1.75}, {"text": "c'est qu'elles n'arrivent", "start": 52.883, "duration": 0.533}, {"text": "pas \u00e0 recruter. Et pourquoi ?", "start": 53.416, "duration": 1.267}, {"text": "Je parlais encore hier avec", "start": 54.683, "duration": 2.266}, {"text": "le directeur de cabinet", "start": 56.949, "duration": 1.084}, {"text": "d'une collectivit\u00e9 locale,", "start": 58.033, "duration": 0.6}, {"text": "qui me disait :", "start": 58.633, "duration": 0.666}, {"text": "\"des gens s'arr\u00eatent de travailler parce que", "start": 59.299, "duration": 1.417}, {"text": "(dans la zone rurale o\u00f9 il est),", "start": 61.933, "duration": 1.65}, {"text": "ils perdent de l'argent", "start": 63.583, "duration": 1.233}, {"text": "\u00e0 aller travailler,", "start": 64.816, "duration": 0.45}, {"text": "parce que le carburant", "start": 65.266, "duration": 0.7}, {"text": "co\u00fbte tellement cher", "start": 65.966, "duration": 0.683}, {"text": "que quand on a besoin de sa voiture", "start": 66.649, "duration": 1.234}, {"text": "pour aller bosser,", "start": 67.883, "duration": 0.866}, {"text": "on ne s'en sort plus.", "start": 68.749, "duration": 0.967}, {"text": "A cette r\u00e9ponse-l\u00e0,", "start": 69.716, "duration": 0.8}, {"text": "encore une fois,", "start": 70.516, "duration": 0.333}, {"text": "je crois que le sujet n'est pas", "start": 70.849, "duration": 1.384}, {"text": "de subventionner le p\u00e9trole,", "start": 72.233, "duration": 1.683}, {"text": "de subventionner la consommation,", "start": 73.916, "duration": 1.767}, {"text": "mais de r\u00e9mun\u00e9rer le travail.", "start": 75.683, "duration": 1.183}, {"text": "C'est le sujet majeur pour nous.", "start": 76.866, "duration": 1.767}]}